[3]:

pc_rm = RenderMesh.deserialize_drm(pc_base_drm)

out_mesh = []
for mesh in pc_rm:
    out = mesh.to_gltf(as_bytes=True, blank_materials=True, apply_scale=True)
    out_mesh.append(out)
